  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. The computational model is evaluated for its ability to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. A full 13-factor assessment is documented: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). The intended use is limited to pre-market regulatory submission supporting 510(k) substantial-equivalence argumentation for adult CPB flow rates of 3–7 L/min at rotational speeds of 2000–3500 RPM. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-fda-gcbp-cfd-v2",
